The input array `arr` is not null.
The length of the input array `arr` is at least 1.
The length of the input array `arr` is at most 500.
Each element in the input array `arr` is an integer.
Each element in the input array `arr` is between 0 and 10^9 (inclusive).
The input integer `k` is at least 1.
The input integer `k` is at most the length of the input array `arr`.
